nsh_rb
Network Shell

Quick and dirty tutorial



sudo apt-get install ruby1.9.3 ##Assuming ubuntu or something along those lines
gem install net-ssh
mkdir -p ~/.nsh/groups
echo 'server1\nserver2' >> ~/.nsh/groups/fakegroup
git clone git://github.com/nburg/nsh_rb.git
cd nsh_rb
./nsh.rb -c uptime -g fakegroup
./nsh.rb -h
